title: CNBC Daily Open: New Trump tariffs are up after U.S. Supreme Court strikes some down
summary_full: The U.S. Supreme Court on Friday struck down much of President Donald Trump's "reciprocal" tariffs. But Trump didn't take their decision lying down.
summary_public: The U.S. Supreme Court on Friday struck down much of President Donald Trump's "reciprocal" tariffs. But Trump didn't take their decision lying down.
